00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:22.829
Hemorrhage in the skin tissue.

00:02:24.650 --> 00:02:26.290
Bruising on the neck.

00:02:27.390 --> 00:02:29.990
Fracture of the greater cornu
of the hyoid bone

00:02:30.110 --> 00:02:31.770
